msItem.note:
This treatise is divided into small sub-sections of 2-3 lines each, and each is prefixed with a symbol for the
                                    most part derived from the Greek alphabet in the following order: cursive minuscule ζ; cursive minsucule δ;
                                    unclear; cursive minuscule θ; θ; open φ; cursive minuscule ψ; unclear; dotted cross.
